Interface CategoryInputBoundary

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CategoryUseCaseInteractor
    public interface CategoryInputBoundary
    CategoryInputBoundary passes in user input of category information in the form of CategoryInputData. Implemented by CategoryUseCaseInteractor.
